{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"reversed","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": like the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}]},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $selection,","                     labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"text":"Suggestions","anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox","isActive":true}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.0.0"}]}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components w